Web Components: Served by express at /WebComponents
Component var icon is resolved as /game-icons-net/{icon} (Served by express)
Buttons:
icon-button include: src="WebComponents/Buttons/IconButton.js" element: icon-button icon="wooden-sign.svg"> A simple 32px button with a white icon. Emits 'icon-click'
holo-button include: src="WebComponents/Buttons/HoloButton.js" element: holo-button icon="android-mask.svg" size="64" icon-color="yellow"> A fun Holographic button. Emits: 'icon-click'

Data Input:
float-field : include: src="" element: float-field  value="3.14" min="0" max="10" step="0.01" placeholder="float">, float input field, Functions: value: get/set, Emits: "change", detail: { value: floatValue }...
int-field :  include: src="" element: int-field value="42" min="0" max="100" step="1"  placeholder="int" >,int input field, Functions: value: get/set, Emits: "change", detail: { value: intValue }...

text-field :  include: src="" element: text-field, text input field, Functions: value: get/set, Emits: "change", detail: { value: intValue }...
select-field :  include: src="" element: select-field, Functions: options: get/set, value: get/set, display: get/set Emits: change", detail: { value: this.value }...
select-field: Use:  <script>
                    const selectField = document.getElementById("selectField");
                    selectField.options = ["Red", "Green", "Blue"];

                    selectField.display = {
                      placeholder: "Pick a color",
                      Red:   { color: "red" },
                      Green: { color: "green" },
                      Blue:  { color: "blue" }
                    };
                </script>

